  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through IREACH project we are supporting Cyclone Amphan affected communities with-
- Unconditional Cash Transfer
- Water Sanitation and Hygiene 
- Conditional Cash Transfer for House repair</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We will take approach of DRR and Build Back Better approach through our response to strengthen community&apos;s capacities. This will help communities to learn to mitigate the risks and impacts of cyclone and floods and also respond immediately. Communities will have capacity and dignity to buy the material from  the cash amount given under project to reduce their sufferings.</narrative>
  </description>
